import React from "react";
import CenteredLayout from "../common/centeredLayout";
import { Button, Checkbox, Form, Select, Input, TextArea } from "semantic-ui-react";

const genderOptions =[
  {key: "m", text: "male", value:"male"},
  {key: "j", text: "female", value:"female"},
  {key: "k", text: "kale", value: "kale"},
  {key: "o", text: "other", value:"other"},
]

const registerRestaurant = () => (
  <CenteredLayout>
  <Form>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Nombre del Restaurante</label>
      <input maxLength="50" placeholder='Nombre del Restaurante' />
    </Form.Field>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Dirección del Restaurante</label>
      <input maxLength="50" placeholder='DirecciÓn del Restaurante' />
    </Form.Field>
    <Form.Field
        control={Select}
        options={genderOptions}
        label={{ children: 'Gender', htmlFor: 'form-select-control-gender' }}
        placeholder='Gender'
        search
        searchInput={{ id: 'form-select-control-gender' }}
    />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field
          control={TextArea}
          label='Información adicional del restaurante'
          placeholder='Tell us more about you...'
    />
    <Form.Field
      control={Input} label="Correo Electrónico"
      maxLength="50" placeholder='Correo Electrónico'
    />
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Dirección de su sitio web</label>
      <input maxLength="50" placeholder='Dirección de su sitio web' />
    </Form.Field>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Teléfono</label>
      <input maxLength="50" placeholder='Teléfono' />
    </Form.Field>
    </Form.Group>
    <Form.Group widths='equal'>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Dirección página de publicidad</label>
      <input maxLength="50" placeholder='Dirección página de publicidad' />
    </Form.Field>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Categoría del Restaurante</label>
      <input maxLength="50" placeholder='Categoría del Restaurante' />
    </Form.Field>
    </Form.Group>

  </Form>
  </CenteredLayout>
)

export default registerRestaurant;
